sh
# Interpreter for: openvpn disconnect <interface>
#
# Default: sh (execute commands immediately)
#
# Disconnect OpenVPN interface and clean up session.
# Outputs shell commands to:
# - Stop OpenVPN daemon
# - Destroy interface
# - Clean up firewall tables
#
# Alternative interpreters:
#   cat         - dry-run (show commands without executing)
#   tee log | sh - log commands and execute
